							<h2>Intra-Company Invoicing : BP </h2>
							<p> POC in progress (Demoed to the UK Partner and planned to be shown to client by mid-June)</p>
							<h3>Problem Statement:</h3>
							<p> Currently British Petroleum handles reconciliation of “non-product” related intra-company transactions manually via a bespoke system that logs all disputed transactions. This leads to manual processes that need chasing down, therefore is labor
								intense and inefficient.
							</p>
							<h3>Proposed Solution:</h3>
							<p> Blockchain based solution to capture the Up-front agreement (UPA) between internal departments and follow it through via transactions such as invoicing between these to avoid disputes and reconciliation. Leading to benefits in terms of FTE reduction
							</p>
						</div>


