							<h2>Automotive Supply Chain Management</h2>
							<p> MVP in progress (Mathew Jones- AAD COC. Planned to be presented @ Partner meet in EU-June)</p>

							<h3>Problem Statement:</h3>
							<p>In the automotive industry, OEM’s plant must interact and coordinate effectively with multiple tiers of suppliers, third party logistics, warehouse and transportation companies to ensure timely delivery of parts and optimized inventory levels.
								In today’s environment, significant challenges exist that prevent these interactions happening seamlessly.</p>

							<h3>Proposed Solution:</h3>
							<p> A Blockchain based system connected with IoT sensors and smart devices would provide permissioned parties in the supply chain with an accurate and transparent end-to-end view of part location, quantity, status and other useful information. This
